OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774285870
OL,3,C'Died fighting for answers': Tributes
OL,4,Cpaid to father of Chinook crash victim
OL,6,FJohn is believed to have been the last
OL,7,Fsurviving parent of anyone who died in
OL,8,Fthe crash, the Chinook Justice
OL,9,FCampaign says.
OL,11,FMinisters met with campaigners, who
OL,12,Fare seeking more answers about the
OL,13,Fcrash, in December. They are due to
OL,14,Fmeet with victims minister Alex Davies-
OL,15,FJones on Wednesday.
OL,17,FNicola Rawcliffe, daughter of John
OL,18,FDockerty and a member of the campaign
OL,19,Fgroup, said: "My father spent the last
OL,20,F32 years wondering why his eldest son
OL,21,Fand my brother, Chris, died.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774285870
OL,3,C'Died fighting for answers': Tributes
OL,4,Cpaid to father of Chinook crash victim
OL,6,F"He died still fighting for answers.
OL,7,FHe campaigned with dignity and
OL,8,Fdetermination, but it is heartbreaking
OL,9,Fthat he has died without the
OL,10,Fgovernment and MoD (Ministry of
OL,11,FDefence) acknowledging the truth about
OL,12,Fthe circumstances surrounding the
OL,13,Fcrash.
OL,15,F"He told me he was disgusted that it
OL,16,Fhas been allowed to fester for as long
OL,17,Fas it has without the government
OL,18,Fgetting to the bottom of things.
OL,20,F"Shame on the MoD for letting yet
OL,21,Fanother relative die without answers."
OL,26,@rD@TpmsD@Hpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
