PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774285870
OL,3,C'Died fighting for answers': Tributes
OL,4,Cpaid to father of Chinook crash victim
OL,6,FMs Rawcliffe, from Diss in Norfolk,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are devastated by the loss
OL,8,Fof my father and horrified that he
OL,9,Fnever saw justice for Chris.
OL,11,F"It is bad enough that a parent has to
OL,12,Fbury their child, but a parent having
OL,13,Fto ask the State as to why they died
OL,14,Fadds insult to injury."
OL,16,FMr Dockerty had released videos
OL,17,Fsupporting the campaign.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
