PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774285870
OL,3,C'Died fighting for answers': Tributes
OL,4,Cpaid to father of Chinook crash victim
OL,6,FHis daughter said she had uncovered
OL,7,Fletters he had written in which he
OL,8,Fsaid he did not believe the pilots
OL,9,Fwere to blame for the crash.
OL,11,FA spokesman for the MoD said: "The
OL,12,FMull of Kintyre crash was a tragic
OL,13,Faccident and our thoughts and
OL,14,Fsympathies remain with the families,
OL,15,Ffriends and colleagues of all those
OL,16,Fwho died.
OL,18,F"We understand that the lack of
OL,19,Fcertainty about the cause of the crash
OL,20,Fhas added to the distress of the
OL,21,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774285870
OL,3,C'Died fighting for answers': Tributes
OL,4,Cpaid to father of Chinook crash victim
OL,6,F"The accident has already been the
OL,7,Fsubject of six inquiries and
OL,8,Finvestigations, including an
OL,9,Findependent judge-led review.
OL,11,F"Defence ministers Lord Coaker,
OL,12,FAlistair Carns and Louise Sandher-
OL,13,FJones met with representatives from
OL,14,Fthe Chinook Justice Campaign in
OL,15,FDecember to listen to their concerns
OL,16,Ffirst-hand."
OL,18,FThe ministry said there has not been
OL,19,Fany evidence presented which would
OL,20,Fshed significant new light on the
OL,21,Fcause of the crash.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
